Class PageSerial

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.contentmine.pdf2svg2.PageSerial
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class PageSerial
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    identifier for page and subcomponents Computer scientists and modules count from 0 Libraries and bibliographers count from 1 This holds both schemes and allows access though named methods Can hold both the page numbers and indexes within the page (subPage, e.g. repeated figures) May also hold other ids (such as Figures, etc.) generally there is a PageSerial for chunks of processed information - pages, images
